title: Guitar Pro 6.1.9 r11686 cw2k
description:
Guitar Pro 6.1.9 r11686 No Activation (Oct 2015)
* Repacked Setup v1 (03.03.2016) [by cw2k] *

* applied Activation Patch to GuitarPro.exe
* included the small soundbank from the demo
  Soundbanks-demo_r11201.gpbank (just additional 120 MB)
  ^- For occasional use the demo-soundbank is a good compromise between 
  installation- & download size + having some RSE sound at all.
  -> Get the GP6 standard Soundbank r370 - 584 MB else where
* put anything of the help files online
  Fixed some really nasty typos and bad grammer crap in the german translation.

* Tools already included in the setup package:
  - GPbank-tool.7z - Add / extracts files from Guitar Pro 6 Soundbank files (*.gpbank):
  - Decompiled GP6-(inno setup script)
